{"title":"php 小数整理,向上取整,向下去整,四舍五入,丢弃小数部分,保留整数部分","date":"2018-07-05T23:23:00.000Z","link":"post/135","categories":["Other"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:16:31.640Z","content":"<p>1.丢弃小数部分,保留整数部分<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">php: intval(7/2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">js:parseInt(7/2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>2.向上取整,有小数就整数部分加1<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">php: ceil(7/2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">js: Math.ceil(7/2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>3.四舍五入<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">php: round(7/2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">js: Math.round(7/2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>4.向下取整<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">php: floor(7/2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">js: Math.floor(7/2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"plsql 永久注册码适用各个版本","link":"post/136"},"next":{"title":"微信小程序获得服务器ip","link":"post/134"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/135/"}